_今起武汉全市范围对居民小区实施封闭管理。
From now on, Wuhan city-wide implementation of closed management of residential areas.
小编身在武汉，响应号召，更要在家安心分析数据。
WwW. zIdiR. coM In Wuhan, to respond to the call, more at home to analyze data.
武汉挺住！_文|《财经》数据研究员 徐进图|视觉中心总监 黎立 编辑|谢丽容1.今日概况2月10日0—24时，31个省（自治区、直辖市）和新疆生产建设兵团报告，新增确诊病例2478例（湖北2097例），新增重症病例849例（湖北839例），新增死亡病例108例（湖北103例，北京、天津、黑龙江、安徽、河南各1例），新增疑似病例3536例（湖北1814例）。
Wuhan Hold Up! Today, at 0-24 p.m., 31 provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the Central Government and the Xinjiang Production and Construction Corps reported 2,478 newly confirmed cases (2,097 in Hubei), 849 new cases (839 in Hubei) and 108 new deaths (103 in Hubei and 1,814 in Hubei).
图12. 新增病例：武汉尚待巩固，其他地区明朗图2国内非湖北地区继续下降。
Figure 12. New cases: Wuhan is yet to be consolidated, other regions are clear Figure 2 domestic non-Hubei continued to decline.
对称形态已基本清晰。
Symmetrical form has been basically clear.
图3湖北非武汉地区继续下降，下降趋势得以巩固。
Fig. 3 Hubei non-Wuhan area continues to decline, the downward trend has been consolidated.
接下来可望形成对称形态，其中2月初孝感、黄冈小“堰塞湖”排洪影响隐约可见。
Next expected to form a symmetrical shape, the beginning of February filial piety, Huanggang small "Yan Sehu" drainage effects looming.
图4武汉数据有好转。
Fig. 4 Wuhan data has improved.
但鉴于此前武汉数据曾多次反复，我们仍须持审慎态度。
But since Wuhan data have been repeated many times before, we still have to be cautious.
数说疫情0209中我们对武汉做出“洪峰可能已过”的乐观估计，有多位武汉网友指出2月8日新增病例下降可能是医院床位受限造成。
According to an optimistic estimate of Wuhan's "possible flood peak may have passed," some Wuhan netizens have pointed out that the February 8 drop in new cases may have been caused by limited hospital beds.
对此我们倾向于采信。
We are inclined to believe it.
我们把这理解为一场艰难的“拉锯战”。
We understand this as a difficult "tug-of-war."
又据人民日报昨日报道：2月10日武汉市领导再次表示全市加大排查和集中救治力度，“截至8日，有确诊重症患者1499人没有得到入院治疗。
"As of February 8, 1,499 patients with severe illnesses had not been hospitalized," Wuhan city leaders said again on Feb. 10, according to the People's Daily.
经过这两天的努力，到今天（2月10日）中午，1499名重症确诊患者已经全部入院”。
By noon today (February 10), 1,499 critically ill patients had been admitted to the hospital.
相信在党中央、中央指导组、省、市党委政府领导下，在全国各方有力支援下，床位、设施和医护人员等关键医疗资源近期会持续陆续到位，追踪、隔离、排查、检测、收治能力全面提高，“堰塞湖”终将化解，疫情终会得到控制。
It is believed that under the leadership of the CPC Central Committee, the Central Steering Group and the provincial and municipal Party committees, and with strong support from all sides, bed, facilities and medical staff will continue to be in place in the near future.
3. 确诊病例增长率：武汉回落，其他地区继续下行图5武汉增长率回落到10%以下。
3. Confirmed case growth rate: Wuhan fell, other regions continue to downward figure 5 Wuhan growth rate fell to below 10%.
湖北非武汉地区下降到5%以下。
Hubei non-Wuhan area fell to less than 5%.
国内非湖北地区继续下降到4%以下。
China's non-Hubei region continued to fall below 4%.
我们对国内非湖北地区和湖北非武汉地区的数据进行分段拟合，同时参考SARS的数据形态，近似推测国内非湖北地区新增确诊病例归零或接近归零的时间为2月24日-26日；湖北非武汉地区新增确诊归零或接近归零的时间应在2月26日-28日。
Based on the data of non-Hubei area and Hubei non-Wuhan area, we estimate the time of zero or close to zero for new confirmed cases in non-Hubei area of China from Feb. 24 to Feb. 26.
对武汉暂不推测。
Wuhan is not speculation.
4. “顶”在何处？我们认为现在可以说说此次疫情的拐点和顶了。
Where is the top We think it is time to talk about the inflection point and peak of the epidemic.
先做一些背景讨论。
Let's start with some background discussion.
数说疫情0206、0207中我们曾讨论过关于“拐点”存在一些分歧。
We discussed some differences on the "inflection point" in the 0206 and 0207 outbreak.
数学定义的拐点在山腰，常识里的拐点在山顶。
Mathematical definition of the inflection point in the mountainside, common sense inflection point at the top.
我们采用常识的说法：山顶。
We use common sense: the top of the mountain.
其实数学的拐点也是顶，只不过是增量的顶。
In fact, the inflection point of mathematics is also the top, is only the increment top.
而常识的拐点是存量本身的顶，也就是增量归零的点。
The inflection point of common sense is the top of the stock itself, which is the point of incremental zero.
数学更有预见性，但常识更直观易感。
Mathematics is more predictable, but common sense is more intuitive.
增量的顶其实大概率已经过了，只待进一步确认了（如前面图2、图3所示）。
The high probability of increments has passed, only to be confirmed further (as shown in Figure 2, Figure 3 above).
常识的顶也即存量的顶还没到来。
The top of common sense, the peak of the stock, has not yet arrived.
我们现在看看这个顶。
Let's look at the top now.
我们讨论三个存量：尚在接受医学观察者、待排查疑似病例数、在院治疗人数。
We discussed three stocks: the number of active medical observers, the number of suspected cases to be cleared, and the number of people in hospital.
这三个存量事关生死，对应大规模行政、社会、医疗资源，对疫情而言相当重要。
These three stocks are a matter of life and death, responding to large-scale administrative, social and medical resources, important for the epidemic.
它们之间有一定的闭环关系（见示意图），所以任何一座大山见顶并开始下降都可能是全面好转的开始。
There is a closed-loop relationship between them (see diagram), so any mountain that peaks and starts to fall could be the beginning of an overall upturn.
图6先看尚在接受医学观察人数。
Figure 6 shows the number of people under medical observation.
图7非湖北地区接受医学观察人数继续呈现下降。
Fig. 7 The number of medical observation patients in non-Hubei areas continued to decrease.
5.待排查疑似病例很多网友一直关心这个数。
Many netizens are concerned about this number all the time.
此前因为湖北没有发布数据，很难进行分析。
Hubei did not release data, it is difficult to carry out analysis.
今天是湖北开始发布此数据的第三天。
Today is the third day Hubei began to release the data.
图8我们看出全国待排查疑似病例第二天出现大幅下降。
Figure 8 shows a significant drop in suspected cases throughout the country the following day.
湖北在9日下降5000多例基础上，继续大幅下降近2000例，显示其排查力度大增。
Hubei dropped more than 5, 000 cases on the 9th, and continued to drop by nearly 2000 cases, showing a sharp increase in its clearance efforts.
非湖北地区也连续两天下降。
Non-Hubei areas also fell for two consecutive days.
与此相关的是密切接触者的追踪能力。
Related to this is the traceability of close contacts.
图9上图可见，非湖北地区一直保持较强追踪力度。
Figure 9 above shows that the non-Hubei region has been a strong tracking efforts.
6. 在院治疗人数图10非湖北区已现见顶迹象，湖北地区住院治疗人数再次出现大幅跳增。
Figure 10 Number of hospital treatment in non-Hubei District has seen the peak signs, Hubei hospital treatment number once again jumped sharply.
印证近几日中央指导组和省、市领导关于加大收治力度、提升救治能力的讲话得以实施。
Confirmed the recent days the central guidance group and provincial and municipal leaders on strengthening treatment capacity to enhance the implementation of the speech.
（还记得武汉市领导昨天说的1499人？）7.新增治愈和病死率图11国内非湖北地区、湖北非武汉地区新治愈人数都在增加。
(Remembering the 1,499 new cases mentioned by Wuhan city leaders yesterday) Figure 11 The number of new patients in non-Hubei and non-Wuhan areas of Hubei is on the increase.
武汉这两天有所回落。
Wuhan has fallen back in the past two days.
图12国内非湖北地区新增治愈人数与新增确诊人数继续接近。
Fig. 12 The number of newly diagnosed patients in non-Hubei areas of China continues to be similar.
据报由于发现散发潜伏期超长病例，有些医疗机构可能将治愈观察期延长。
It has been reported that some medical institutions may extend the period of therapeutic observation due to the discovery of cases with an excess incubation period.
有可能延缓新增治愈人数增长，导致交叉点推后到来。
It is possible to delay the growth of new healers, causing intersections to be delayed.
图13病死率持续小幅回升。
Figure 13 The mortality rate continues to rise slightly.
很多网友对这一变动表示担心。
Many netizens expressed concern about the change.
我们初步认为这主要是疫情不同阶段分子分母变动不同步造成，当属正常。
We initially believe that this is mainly due to the different stages of the epidemic molecular denominator change is not synchronized, when it is normal.
小结：武汉“堰塞湖”正在有力化解。
Summary: Wuhan "Yan Sehu" is a powerful solution.
虽难免反复，但趋势已明。
Though inevitable, the trend is clear.
国内非湖北地区、湖北非武汉地区持续向好。
China's non-Hubei region, Hubei non-Wuhan region continued to improve.
疫情之顶已露端倪。
The pinnacle of the epidemic is in sight.
